						<h2>Yemen</h2>
						<img src="img/unitar1.png" width="200"></img>
						<p>In Yemen, UNOSAT is helping an NGO to improve water usage by mapping agricultural areas using sattelite imagery.
							Help us find photos from the web using the firefox Geotag-X plugin. Photos or videos of coffee and qat (also spelt
							khat) crops in the area are particularly helpful, as well as any assessment of soil conditions or drought stress.</p>
						<p>With your help, UNOSAT can quickly build a photo library to assist with satellite imagery interpretation.</p>
					</div>
